org.apache.polygene.library.constraints.annotation

Annotation Type HostPortList


  • @ConstraintDeclaration
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Constraints(value=HostPortListConstraint.class)
public @interface HostPortList
    Marks a property as being a string, with a comma or space separated list of "host:port", where host is a valid hostname, IPv4 address or IPv6 address and port is in the range of 0 to 65535
